{"content": "<h2>The Artist: Will A.K.</h2>\t\t\n\t\t<p>Will is short for Willhelm Ardylles Kurniawan or willak.eth for his collectoors. An Indonesian autodidact who basically lives on a highway of superflat aesthetics, fiction-as-life, and absurdist vibes. Will pulls from the superflat tradition but makes it way messier—less polished, more personal. The dude’s whole thing is turning the banal into a caricature of itself, so it loops back into feeling meaningful again (maybe).</p>\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figure>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img width=\"722\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2025/01/bathingfrominwarmwaterwill-722x1024.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2025/01/bathingfrominwarmwaterwill-722x1024.png 722w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2025/01/bathingfrominwarmwaterwill-211x300.png 211w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2025/01/bathingfrominwarmwaterwill-768x1090.png 768w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2025/01/bathingfrominwarmwaterwill-1082x1536.png 1082w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2025/01/bathingfrominwarmwaterwill-1443x2048.png 1443w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2025/01/bathingfrominwarmwaterwill-1320x1873.png 1320w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2025/01/bathingfrominwarmwaterwill-600x851.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 722px) 100vw, 722px\" />\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figcaption>Bathing Frog in Lukewarm Water by Will A.K.</figcaption>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</figure>\n\t\t\t<h2>The Collection: 1 of 1s</h2>\t\t\n\t\t<p>Will's 1 of 1s are a ride of wild colors and deceptively \"flat\" visuals that feel layered AF when you actually look deeper. The fiction-vs-reality thing isn’t subtle...and that’s the point. He’s like, “what if life is a cartoon and we’re all NPCs?” ...which is a funny way to deal with postmodern despair tbh. If Will is trying to say anything, it’s probably that absurdity doesn’t cancel meaning—it just makes the search for it weirder, which kinda slaps.</p>\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figure>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img width=\"749\" height=\"703\" src=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2025/01/Screenshot-2025-01-16-at-3.16.37 PM-1024x961.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2025/01/Screenshot-2025-01-16-at-3.16.37 PM-1024x961.png 1024w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2025/01/Screenshot-2025-01-16-at-3.16.37 PM-300x281.png 300w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2025/01/Screenshot-2025-01-16-at-3.16.37 PM-768x720.png 768w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2025/01/Screenshot-2025-01-16-at-3.16.37 PM-1320x1238.png 1320w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2025/01/Screenshot-2025-01-16-at-3.16.37 PM-600x563.png 600w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2025/01/Screenshot-2025-01-16-at-3.16.37 PM.png 1356w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 749px) 100vw, 749px\" />\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figcaption>Will A.K. 1 of 1s from 27 1/1s minted on SuperRare</figcaption>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</figure>\n\t\t\t<h2>A Specific Artwork: Two Figures</h2>\t\t\n\t\t<p>Two Figures is more roughed up with the polish giving way to burnished edges and buffed away surfaces. Minted in January 2023 as one of 5 works in the 'Flat No More' collection. The green grass is given a degree of depth that his previous superflat thinking had denied. There is a dance of sorts between the two central characters in 'Two Figures'. On the left perhaps an invitation...and the right perhaps a moment to consider said invitation... all while a row of NPC cartoons watch on from the edge of the yellow stage. <a href=\"https://giftshop.theline.wtf/token/ETHEREUM:0x43ffea8a49b55c90f91b713c8e2fcf3e55a6f5b9:1\">Two Figures is available in The Line Gift Shop for 0.5 eth.</a></p>\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figure>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img width=\"749\" height=\"999\" src=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2025/01/TwoFigures-768x1024.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2025/01/TwoFigures-768x1024.png 768w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2025/01/TwoFigures-225x300.png 225w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2025/01/TwoFigures-1152x1536.png 1152w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2025/01/TwoFigures-1536x2048.png 1536w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2025/01/TwoFigures-400x533.png 400w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2025/01/TwoFigures-1320x1760.png 1320w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2025/01/TwoFigures-600x800.png 600w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2025/01/TwoFigures.png 1800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 749px) 100vw, 749px\" />\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figcaption>Two Figures by Will A.K. minted Jan 2023</figcaption>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</figure>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"https://theline.wtf/listing/will-a-k/\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img width=\"749\" height=\"477\" src=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2025/01/Screenshot-2025-01-16-at-3.37.38 PM-1024x652.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2025/01/Screenshot-2025-01-16-at-3.37.38 PM-1024x652.png 1024w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2025/01/Screenshot-2025-01-16-at-3.37.38 PM-300x191.png 300w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2025/01/Screenshot-2025-01-16-at-3.37.38 PM-768x489.png 768w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2025/01/Screenshot-2025-01-16-at-3.37.38 PM-1536x979.png 1536w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2025/01/Screenshot-2025-01-16-at-3.37.38 PM-2048x1305.png 2048w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2025/01/Screenshot-2025-01-16-at-3.37.38 PM-1320x841.png 1320w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2025/01/Screenshot-2025-01-16-at-3.37.38 PM-600x382.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 749px) 100vw, 749px\" />\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"https://theline.wtf/listing/will-a-k/\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tWill A.K. | Line 836\n\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"https://giftshop.theline.wtf/token/ETHEREUM:0x43ffea8a49b55c90f91b713c8e2fcf3e55a6f5b9:1\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tExit via The Line Gift Shop\n\t\t\t\t\t</a>"}